sequenceDiagram
    participant CLI as ge CLI
    participant GW as Cloud Run gateway
    participant CT as Cloud Tasks queue
    participant W as Cloud Run worker
    participant L as Firestore + AlloyDB ledger

    CLI->>GW: build --remote (gcloud identity token)
    GW->>CT: enqueue stage task
    loop one stage at a time, self-advancing
        CT->>W: deliver task (OIDC, runner SA)
        W->>L: record stage event
        W->>CT: enqueue next stage
    end
    L-->>CLI: run observable live (console, ge ledger tail)
